29static INLINE VP9_REFFRAME
30ref_frame_to_vp9_reframe(vpx_ref_frame_type_t frame) {
31 switch (frame) {
32 case VP8_LAST_FRAME: return VP9_LAST_FLAG;
33 case VP8_GOLD_FRAME: return VP9_GOLD_FLAG;
34 case VP8_ALTR_FRAME: return VP9_ALT_FLAG;
35 }
36 assert(0 && "Invalid Reference Frame");
37 return VP9_LAST_FLAG;
38}
